quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  7,12,"Wathi (uAllâh): “Yintoni na ekuthinteleyo wena (Iblîs) ukuba uqubude Ndakuba Ndikuyalele?” UIblîs wathi: “Mna ndingcono kunaye (uAdam), mna Undidale ngomlilo, yena wamdala ngodongwe.”"
  7,13,"Wathi(uAllâh):“Hinina Iblîs!Yihla, umkeapha,Ayikokwakho ukuba ukhukhumale apha. Phuma umke apha kuba wena (ngoku) ungomnye wabo banyelekileyo, bahlazekileyo"
  7,14,"(UIblîs) wathi: “Ndinike urhoxiselo lwesohlwayo kude kube (yiMini) yokuvuswa kwabafileyo"
  7,15,"Wathi (uAllâh): “Wena ungomnye wabo barhoxiselweyo isohlwayo.”"
  7,16,"(UIblîs) wathi: “Ngenxa yokuba Undibeke ekulahlekeni, inene mna ndiya (kuncathama) ndibalalele eNdleleni yaKho ethe Tye"
  7,17,"Kananjalo xa ndibafikele (ndabavela) ngaphambili nangemva kwabo, ekunene kwabo nasekhohlo kwabo. Wena akuyi kufumana uninzi lwabo lunombulelo (kuWe)"
  7,18,"Wathi (uAllâh): “Phuma umke apha uhlazekile ungogxothiweyo. Nabani na (ebantwini) oya kulandela wena, inene Mna Ndiya kuzalisa isiHogo ngani nonke"
  7,19,"Ke wena Adam! Hlala wena nomkakho ePaladesi, nidle nobabini apho nithande khona ukukudla kodwa, ningasondeli kuwo lo umthi, ngapha koko nobabini niya kuba ngabagabadeli”"
  7,20,"Waza uShaytân wabasebezela bobabini iingcebiso [zakhe (esenzela)] ukuveza oko kwakufihliwe kubo kuziindawo (zomzimba wabo) ezinqabileyo, wathi: “INkosi yenu Ayinalelanga nje (ukuba ningadli) kulo mthi koko nina nokusuka\tnibe\tziingelosi\tkungenjalo\tnibe\tngabaphila ngonaphakade.”"
  7,21,"Kananjalo (uShayatân) wafunga ngoAllâh kubo bobabini (wathi): “Inene mna ndingomnye wabaninqwenelela okuhle nobabini ngokunyanisekileyo.”"
  7,22,"Wabalahlekisakengokongenkohliso. Bathibesakukungcamla okomthi lowo, (kwasuka) oko kwakukade kufihlakele kubo kwabonakala kubo, baqalisa ukuzigquma ngamagqabi emithi yasePaladesi (ukufihla ubuze babo). Ke kaloku iNkosi yabo yabuza kubo: “Andinalelanga na ngalo mthi, Ndanixelela kananjalo ukuba ngenene uShaytân ulutshaba lwenu olucacileyo”"